des:
Philip blue wave resistor talks about political opinions on diverse news and events all around us.

We are in a very noisy world with lots of events on the glob are affecting us. Philip blue wave resistor will post interesting views on political and international issues trending today.

[How to use]
You can say, “Alexa, open Philip blue wave resistor” to hear the latest stories. While listening to a story, you can say ”Alexa, stop” to stop the story. You can continue to the next story by answering “Yes” to the question “Would you like to read the next post?"

Example phrase:
"Alexa, open Philip blue wave resistor"

[Dialogue flow]
a. The Skill will play its welcome message upon hearing the user’s command, “Alexa, open Philip blue wave resistor."
b. The Skill will automatically play the most recent posting from the open Philip blue wave resistor board from wecast.ai.
c.After playing the most recent post, the Skill will ask “Would you like to read the next post?”
- If the listener says “Yes”, the Skill will play the next posting
- If the listener says “No”, the Skill will exit the Skill
